970
01:14:15,335 --> 01:14:17,022
This is your team, son.

971
01:14:18,203 --> 01:14:19,707
You make the call.

972
01:14:30,451 --> 01:14:32,292
Red 2, this is Pegasus actual.

973
01:14:32,416 --> 01:14:35,807
Get the XO, get your men
and get to the evac coordinates.

974
01:14:35,969 --> 01:14:38,562
<i>Secure your men,
and detonate the warhead</i>

975
01:14:38,736 --> 01:14:40,044
<i>using the manual trigger.</i>

976
01:14:41,590 --> 01:14:43,653
Complete your mission, Captain.

977
01:14:45,469 --> 01:14:46,522
Understood.

978
01:14:47,247 --> 01:14:49,965
- Sergeant! Get ready to move out.
- Yes, Sir.

979
01:14:50,085 --> 01:14:53,383
All right, now get on your feet,
and I'll get you out of here.

980
01:14:58,284 --> 01:15:00,659
Come on everybody move,
it's time, let's go!

981
01:15:00,779 --> 01:15:02,071
Get your suits on.

982
01:15:02,546 --> 01:15:04,199
Come on, go, go, go!

983
01:15:11,223 --> 01:15:12,961
You too, Major. Let's get...

984
01:15:14,737 --> 01:15:15,888
You too, Captain.

985
01:15:17,278 --> 01:15:18,891
Leave the nuke, if you don't mind.

986
01:15:19,678 --> 01:15:21,587
What the frak are you doing?

987
01:15:22,140 --> 01:15:23,811
Completing the mission.

988
01:15:25,243 --> 01:15:26,295
Take it.

989
01:15:26,548 --> 01:15:28,281
I don't need it anymore.

990
01:15:28,627 --> 01:15:29,515
Major.

991
01:15:30,438 --> 01:15:32,573
I just gave you an order, soldier.

992
01:15:33,283 --> 01:15:34,835
Unless you wanna die,

993
01:15:34,990 --> 01:15:37,201
I suggest you obey it. Go.

994
01:15:51,019 --> 01:15:51,834
Why?

995
01:15:52,825 --> 01:15:54,481
You know damn well why.

996
01:15:55,556 --> 01:15:57,638
Put on your suit,
you're about to run out of air.

997
01:16:12,646 --> 01:16:14,194
<i>It's been an honor, Captain.</i>

998
01:16:43,358 --> 01:16:45,700
<i>All this has happened before</i>

999
01:16:46,391 --> 01:16:48,414
<i>and will happen again.</i>

1000
01:16:54,627 --> 01:16:58,159
<i>Come in, Major. I've been
waiting for you for a long time.</i>

1001
01:17:05,211 --> 01:17:07,194
You're what all this is about,
aren't you?

1002
01:17:09,530 --> 01:17:10,661
What are you?

1003
01:17:11,235 --> 01:17:13,045
What am I? A man.

1004
01:17:14,461 --> 01:17:16,384
Or am I a machine?

1005
01:17:19,704 --> 01:17:22,473
Our children will live by our God.

1006
01:17:24,661 --> 01:17:25,673
Are you...

1007
01:17:26,386 --> 01:17:27,397
a god?

1008
01:17:27,638 --> 01:17:29,371
I have seen things,

1009
01:17:30,385 --> 01:17:32,608
your life, Kendra Shaw,

1010
01:17:33,099 --> 01:17:34,606
the things you've done...

1011
01:17:35,338 --> 01:17:37,421
the things you felt you had to do...

1012
01:17:37,541 --> 01:17:39,589
all leading to this moment.

1013
01:17:41,074 --> 01:17:43,828
You wish to be forgiven, my child.

1014
01:17:46,242 --> 01:17:47,252
I repeat!

1015
01:17:47,841 --> 01:17:50,656
We will carry out this order!

1016
01:17:50,776 --> 01:17:52,628
We will shoot these people!

1017
01:17:55,340 --> 01:17:56,896
What are we doing, Sir?

1018
01:17:57,273 --> 01:17:58,074
Sir?

1019
01:18:48,474 --> 01:18:50,436
Do you wish to be forgiven?

1020
01:18:56,399 --> 01:18:59,134
- Yes.
- Then, come closer.

1021
01:18:59,440 --> 01:19:01,489
There's something I have to tell you.

1022
01:19:04,240 --> 01:19:05,042
Come.

1023
01:19:22,904 --> 01:19:26,699
Kara Thrace will lead
the human race to its end.

1024
01:19:28,561 --> 01:19:31,825
- What?
- She is the herald of the Apocalypse.

1025
01:19:32,179 --> 01:19:34,301
The harbinger of death.

1026
01:19:34,572 --> 01:19:36,524
They must not follow her.

1027
01:19:43,224 --> 01:19:46,829
<i>Pegasus, evac Raptor inbound.
Extraction complete. Cleared Baseship.</i>

1028
01:19:46,949 --> 01:19:48,976
Raptor is on its way back, Sir.

1029
01:19:49,718 --> 01:19:52,878
They have Starbuck aboard.
Major Shaw stayed behind.

1030
01:19:56,544 --> 01:19:57,336
Starbuck?

1031
01:19:58,384 --> 01:19:59,540
<i>Actual.</i>

1032
01:20:00,931 --> 01:20:02,180
<i>This is Red 1.</i>

1033
01:20:02,887 --> 01:20:03,901
<i>Come in.</i>

1034
01:20:04,443 --> 01:20:07,602
- Red 1, this is Pegasus Actual. Report.
<i>- Commander?</i>

1035
01:20:08,509 --> 01:20:09,759
<i>I gotta warn you.</i>

1036
01:20:09,900 --> 01:20:11,598
<i>It's Captain Thrace.</i>

1037
01:20:14,061 --> 01:20:16,480
- Red 1, report!
- They're jamming us again, Sir.

1038
01:20:16,812 --> 01:20:19,700
- Red 1, this is Actual, come in!
- We lost her.

1039
01:20:27,317 --> 01:20:28,331
Actual.

1040
01:20:30,052 --> 01:20:31,066
Come in.

1041
01:20:32,245 --> 01:20:33,164
Actual.

1042
01:20:35,928 --> 01:20:38,957
As my own existence comes to a close,

1043
01:20:40,195 --> 01:20:43,578
only to begin a new,
in ways... uncertain.

1044
01:20:49,123 --> 01:20:51,056
You're scared,
aren't you, mother-frakker?

1045
01:20:55,252 --> 01:20:56,643
You should be.

1046
01:20:57,397 --> 01:20:59,424
All this has happened before.

1047
01:21:00,214 --> 01:21:01,699
And will happen again.

1048
01:21:02,642 --> 01:21:03,491
Again.

1049
01:22:06,460 --> 01:22:08,208
You wanted to see me, Admiral.

1050
01:22:09,545 --> 01:22:11,101
Thank you for coming in.

1051
01:22:12,669 --> 01:22:14,437
Starbuck was here a little earlier.

1052
01:22:17,408 --> 01:22:19,145
She's recommended major Shaw

1053
01:22:19,306 --> 01:22:21,063
for a posthumous commendation.

1054
01:22:22,301 --> 01:22:24,108
She wasn't looking for medals.

1055
01:22:24,567 --> 01:22:25,753
No, she wasn't.

1056
01:22:27,304 --> 01:22:29,358
But I've been going through Cain's logs,

1057
01:22:30,293 --> 01:22:31,809
and from a tactical perspective,

1058
01:22:31,929 --> 01:22:34,783
it's hard to find a fault
in anything that she did,

1059
01:22:35,194 --> 01:22:36,631
or that Kendra did.

1060
01:22:37,326 --> 01:22:39,197
They butchered innocent civilians, Dad.

1061
01:22:43,189 --> 01:22:44,204
Come on.

1062
01:22:44,638 --> 01:22:46,189
How can you ignore that?

1063
01:22:46,736 --> 01:22:50,432
I know that I didn't have to face
any of the situations that she did.

1064
01:22:51,025 --> 01:22:52,964
I had the President in my face,

1065
01:22:53,203 --> 01:22:55,860
arguing for the survival
of the civilian fleet,

1066
01:22:56,853 --> 01:22:59,659
I had colonel Tigh to keep me honest,

1067
01:23:00,389 --> 01:23:03,720
balancing my morality and my tactics,
and I had you.

1068
01:23:05,316 --> 01:23:06,685
Now...

1069
01:23:07,392 --> 01:23:10,722
you don't have any children,
so you might not understand this,

1070
01:23:11,065 --> 01:23:13,848
but you see yourself
reflected in their eyes.

1071
01:23:15,216 --> 01:23:18,661
And there are some things that
I thought of doing, with this fleet.

1072
01:23:20,919 --> 01:23:22,635
But I stopped myself because I knew

1073
01:23:22,755 --> 01:23:25,219
that I'd have to face you
the following day.

1074
01:23:32,255 --> 01:23:33,886
If you hadn't been in CIC,

1075
01:23:36,304 --> 01:23:38,335
I would have ordered that strike.

1076
01:23:38,939 --> 01:23:41,676
Kara would be dead,
so would the rest of the team.

1077
01:23:42,201 --> 01:23:43,660
You did nothing wrong,

1078
01:23:44,185 --> 01:23:45,406
neither did I.

1079
01:23:46,957 --> 01:23:50,448
We both made decisions that we had to,
to accomplish our missions.

1080
01:23:51,531 --> 01:23:52,352
Yeah.

1081
01:23:54,291 --> 01:23:55,181
Cain.

1082
01:23:56,538 --> 01:23:57,725
Kendra.

1083
01:23:59,800 --> 01:24:01,009
Were they wrong?

1084
01:24:02,538 --> 01:24:04,751
And if I believed in the Gods,

1085
01:24:05,104 --> 01:24:07,753
I'd say they'll be judged
by a high power.

1086
01:24:08,263 --> 01:24:09,974
But since you don't believe...

1087
01:24:11,924 --> 01:24:14,593
Then history will have
to make its judgments.

1088
01:24:18,925 --> 01:24:22,011
And since history's first draft
will be written in our logs...

1089
01:24:26,525 --> 01:24:28,860
Well, I guess
I've got some writing to do.

1090
01:24:32,410 --> 01:24:35,107
You'll write that commendation.

1091
01:24:37,519 --> 01:24:38,734
Yeah, I will.

1092
01:25:07,283 --> 01:25:09,106
Not a lot to show for a life, huh?

1093
01:25:10,738 --> 01:25:11,783
I guess not.

1094
01:25:13,956 --> 01:25:15,741
Do you have any idea why she did it?

1095
01:25:19,215 --> 01:25:21,360
Maybe she thought
she had a lot to answer for.

1096
01:25:22,823 --> 01:25:24,204
Maybe she had it coming...

1097
01:25:27,416 --> 01:25:28,897
We've all got it coming.

1098
01:25:33,961 --> 01:25:36,145
You might as well hear this from me.

1099
01:25:37,797 --> 01:25:39,866
I've asked to be reassigned
to Galactica.

1100
01:25:42,044 --> 01:25:43,088
Any reason?

1101
01:25:43,876 --> 01:25:46,401
You might say that I've a beef
with my commanding officer.

1102
01:25:48,347 --> 01:25:49,714
And... what's that?

1103
01:25:50,967 --> 01:25:52,998
That mother-frakker keeps
trying to get me killed.

1104
01:25:56,321 --> 01:25:58,210
Oh, you ever think you might deserve it?

1105
01:25:59,610 --> 01:26:01,616
Speak for yourself, Lee, I...

1106
01:26:01,736 --> 01:26:02,913
have a destiny.

1107
01:26:03,787 --> 01:26:05,989
Had my palm read by a Cylon, remember?

1108
01:26:06,483 --> 01:26:07,888
A destiny, right?

1109
01:26:08,448 --> 01:26:10,926
You better believe that. So I guess, you

1110
01:26:11,049 --> 01:26:13,004
are stuck with me till the end.

1111
01:26:13,916 --> 01:26:16,004
I gotta go break in your new CAG,

1112
01:26:16,897 --> 01:26:17,732
Sir.

